### 会員登録
POST http://localhost:8080/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "testuser",
  "name": "テストユーザー",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}
### ログイン成功
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "testuser",
  "password": "password"
}
### ログイン失敗
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "testuser",
  "password": "abc"
}